title: KSI vs. Logan Paul 2
overview: KSI vs. Logan Paul 2 is an professional boxing match between the British YouTuber Olajide "JJ" Olatunji (known online as KSI), and American YouTuber, Logan Paul. Both fighters will be making their professional boxing debuts. The fight constitutes a rematch of the previous white-collar amateur boxing fight between the two, which ended in a majority draw. The fight is set to take place at the Staples Center, Los Angeles on 9 November 2019.
